Glover will be joined by Alden Ehrenreich, who will play the young Solo in Star Wars Celebration in July.The film will show Calrissian in his younger years as a scoundrel on the rise in the galaxy's underworld - years before the events involving Han, Leia and Darth Vader in The Empire Strikes Back and his rise to Rebel Alliance hero in Return of the Jedi.The still-untitled Han Solo film will be directed by Lego Movie directors Phil Lord and Christopher Miller. It will be released in 2018.